Variable 𝒢:𝖦𝗋𝗈𝗎𝗉 provisionally

Variable o:𝖮𝗉𝖾𝗋𝖺𝗍𝗂𝗈𝗇

Variable f:𝖤𝗅𝖾𝗆𝖾𝗇𝗍
Variable g:𝖤𝗅𝖾𝗆𝖾𝗇𝗍

Variable 𝑋:𝖮𝖻𝗃𝖾𝖼𝗍

Axiom (GroupCategoryMorphisms)
  f is an element of 𝒢 𝗂𝖿𝖿 𝝻_f:*_𝒢 ⟶ *_𝒢 in 𝘊_𝒢

Axiom (GroupCategoryObjects)
  𝑋 is an object of 𝘊_𝒢 𝗂𝖿𝖿 𝑋 = *_𝒢

Axiom (GroupCategoryComposition)
  Suppose
    f is an element of 𝒢
    g is an element of 𝒢
    o is an operation of 𝒢
  Then
    𝝻_f;𝝻_g = 𝝻_(g o f)
